products.description: 10th Gen Intel Core i9-10900F desktop processor without processor graphics. Features Intel Turbo Boost Max Technology 3.0. Built for the everyday desktop user; this processor delivers amazing performance for everything from enthusiast gaming and creation to productivity. Discrete graphics required.
